      "citation_id": "[CITATION_6]",
      "span_text": "More recently, partially coherent RP beam with variable spatial coherence was generated in experiment, and it was found that we can shape the beam profile of the focused RP beam by varying its initial spatial coherence, which is useful for material thermal processing and particle trapping."
